					"body": "PR: https://github.com/appcelerator/alloy/pull/844\r\n\r\nFor themed project, {{app/themes/<theme>/DefaultIcon.png}} will be copied to project root by alloy compile. If theme doesn't exist or no theme is configured, {{app/DefaultIcon.png}} will be copied. \r\n\r\nThis does require existing apps to move {{DefaultIcon.png}} from project root to {{/app}} directory.",
